{"prayers":[{"phelps":"AB02304TST","text":"Nu vo ada han e cuda e Tanawa Tanawa e wap pie-it nush ta Weed cada my a too Wee a Ma tu queet me quash  me quash cada e auta quan eada we how ta quan Kaden ought to quan qua e hoeta quan sa Wee e whan e cua Cada oo we qad me on ich, e Wab wut e Na did quay, e New casa e wa nu in.\n\n* I bear witness, O my God, that Thou hast created me to know Thee and to worship Thee. I testify, at this moment, to my powerlessness and to Thy might, to my poverty and to Thy wealth.\n* There is none other God but Thee, the Help in Peril, the Self-Subsisting.","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"246ca368-d0c6-4372-b545-7bd86aee1c68","book_cats":{"ar":{"cat":"النيروز","order_in_cat":4},"bn":{"cat":"মহান বা’ব-এর জন্মদিনের ফলকলিপি","order_in_cat":1},"de":{"cat":"Das mittlere Pflichtgebet","order_in_cat":1},"en":{"cat":"Birth of The Báb","order_in_cat":2},"fa":{"cat":"الواح ایام صیام","order_in_cat":2},"is":{"cat":"Lofgjörð og þökk","order_in_cat":7},"kl":{"cat":"Aalajaassuseq","order_in_cat":1},"lt":{"cat":"Išbandymai ir sunkumai","order_in_cat":3},"ml":{"cat":"പ്രബോധനം","order_in_cat":7},"nl":{"cat":"Lof en dankbaarheid","order_in_cat":6},"no":{"cat":"Besøkelsens tavle","order_in_cat":1},"pl":{"cat":"Ornamenty","order_in_cat":1},"ro":{"cat":"Zilele Intercalare","order_in_cat":2}},"translations":[{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"lg","lang_name":"Ganda"},{"language":"no","lang_name":"Norwegian"},{"language":"is","lang_name":"Icelandic"},{"language":"lt","lang_name":"Lithuanian"},{"language":"bn","lang_name":"Bengali"},{"language":"bs","lang_name":"Bosnian"},{"language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"language":"kl","lang_name":"Kalaallisut"},{"language":"eu","lang_name":"Basque"},{"language":"ht","lang_name":"Haitian Creole"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"ml","lang_name":"Malayalam"},{"language":"nl","lang_name":"Dutch"},{